{"tid":1535462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位記者唔好再播再跟警察個記者會","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:32:51.000Z","uid":61545,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"390d053a95989b52d4863624e1669f89209832f0","tid":1535462,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"【16:20】今早被警員撲倒的男學生傷勢頗重，多名同學放學後前往醫院探望，其中有同學透露受傷的中三男同學嘴唇縫了針，但因被撲倒而失去兩隻門牙。<br />\n<br />\n【警暴伸校園 撐罷課學生遭軍裝撲跌爆嘴甩2門牙】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/30WuXte\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30WuXte&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=8974d77a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/30WuXte</a><br />\n【警方辯稱因「地面濕滑」跌倒】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Uoyr5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Uoyr5g&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=143f6c82\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Uoyr5g</a><br />\n【女校長首開腔強調沒報警 同學：說法不可信﻿】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Uzcil3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Uzcil3&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=9378f436\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Uzcil3</a><br />\n<br />\n條片斷正都可以講大話<br />\n啲藍絲唔分析，睇電視當真理<br />\n結果個記者會變相維穩大會<br />\n清醒嘅人會睇到嬲<br />\nOn9嘅信到十足<br />\n即使啲記者係戰線影到幾多有力證據都冇用<br />\n班恐怖份子都改哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb5d434e6498c7940a6beda43b93f5c7c8ac71b","tid":1535462,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f40047b34b04852a37cf567fd3c33880ccbfc28","tid":1535462,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:07:09.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"2ce185d2d5d0d71aa81ff2ba4524604baa043068","tid":1535462,"uid":61545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ef9ebdc3f0ca89c9acdf729076c569ddb619a8","tid":1535462,"uid":61545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"間接幫恐怖份子宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db28b20814e176e39d13e2c9a642045a5e45e6e9","tid":1535462,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:11:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6510a080e8674872bb6d5ad066aeaa276e2055c","tid":1535462,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa8dd3130557085c808e67002ba336a8ec53cc9a","tid":1535462,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48df11ccb5